Scholar FAQ How can I see my fairy&rsquo;s nameplate in battle?
A. Character Configuration &gt; Control Settings &gt; &ldquo;Target&rdquo; tab &gt; Under &ldquo;Target Settings&rdquo;, Uncheck &ldquo;Disable targeting of pets and minions when in battle.&rdquo;
B. Character Config &gt; Display Name Settings &gt; &ldquo;Own&rdquo; tab &gt; Under &ldquo;Pets&rdquo; set &ldquo;Display Name Settings&rdquo; to &ldquo;Always&rdquo; or &ldquo;During Battle&rdquo;
Both options must be set this way or your fairy&rsquo;s nameplate will be hidden.

For your Best-in-Slot gear, you will generally be going for;
Weapon Damage Dexterity Crit Direct Hit Determination Skill Speed This is not 100% exact once you get to the max gear, but until you have that, that is the priority in stats.
For non-BIS pieces: Crit &raquo;&raquo; DH &gt; DET &raquo;&raquo;&raquo;&raquo;&raquo; SkS
